title: Al McGlashan's Fish'n with Mates
overview: Al McGlashan is hell bent on sharing his incredible experiences with fishing mates the world over. Fish'n with Mates sees him ticking off items from his personal fishing bucket list including chasing Jurassic tuna on Ascension Island with astronauts, catching jumping tarpon in The Everglades and ripping it with international bass-pro Carl Jocumsen.
